OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FWords by Emily Youlton, Senior
OL,7,FPolitics Producer
OL,9,FAndy Burnham has become the UK's
OL,10,Fseventh British prime minister in ten
OL,11,Fyears after meeting the King on Monday
OL,12,Fmorning.
OL,14,FKeir Starmer, who stood down as party
OL,15,Fleader in June, gave his official
OL,16,Fresignation to the King on Monday and,
OL,17,Ffollowing a short speech in Downing
OL,18,FStreet, waved goodbye to No 10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FIn his final PMQs, Starmer defended
OL,7,Fhis record in government, saying he
OL,8,Fwas "proud to leave this country in a
OL,9,Fbetter shape than I found it".
OL,11,FBut Starmer's downfall was
OL,12,Fprecipitated by his MPs' frustration
OL,13,Fat what they saw as the slow pace of
OL,14,Fchange under his leadership.
OL,16,FThe pressure is now on Burnham from
OL,17,Fall sides of the Labour Party to
OL,18,Fdeliver on a wide range of policies,
OL,19,Fto unlock UK growth and to restore
OL,20,Fstability.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FBurnham has made known his bold plans
OL,7,Ffor devolution, including a No 10 of
OL,8,Fthe North, and has promised "good
OL,9,Fgrowth in every postcode".
OL,11,FBut for all his ambition in that area,
OL,12,Fthere are plenty of other issues that
OL,13,Frequire Burnham's attention.
OL,15,FHere's a look at Burnham's bulging in-
OL,16,Ftray - from foreign policy and
OL,17,Fimmigration to housing and welfare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
