PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe government's failure to tackle the
OL,12,Fcountry's growing benefits bill was
OL,13,Fconsidered one of the outgoing prime
OL,14,Fminister's most damaging missteps.
OL,16,FStarmer struggled with a rebellion
OL,17,Ffrom his own party against a benefits
OL,18,Fsystem overhaul because of concerns
OL,19,Fover how the changes would affect
OL,20,Fpeople with disabilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
