CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThe policy, like several others, ended
OL,7,Fin a U-turn.
OL,9,FIt now falls to Burnham and his
OL,10,Fchancellor to balance the books, while
OL,11,Fkeeping Labour MPs on side. Burnham
OL,12,Fwill be in office when the final
OL,13,Frecommendations of the Timms review
OL,14,Finto disability benefits are
OL,15,Fpublished. The interim report claimed
OL,16,Fthat personal independence payment
OL,17,F(Pip) "is no longer fit for purpose".
OL,26,@yD@GOUyD@dO]
