OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThe total spend for 2025-2026 forecast
OL,7,Fis #322.6 billion, more than 23% of
OL,8,Fthe government's total spend, with
OL,9,Fmore than half - around #177.7 billion
OL,10,Fthis year - spent on pensioners.
OL,12,FBurnham has already confirmed that he
OL,13,Fwill not scrap the triple lock on
OL,14,Fstate pensions, which raises the
OL,15,Fpension rate each year by the highest
OL,16,Frate of either inflation, average wage
OL,17,Fgrowth, or 2.5%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
