OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FOther benefit challenges include an
OL,7,Fincreasing number of people claiming
OL,8,Fsickness benefits, as well as record
OL,9,Fyouth unemployment.
OL,11,FThe recent Milburn report found that
OL,12,Fmore than one million young people (16-
OL,13,F24 year olds) are currently not in
OL,14,Feducation, employment or training
OL,15,F(Neet).
OL,17,FBurnham has spoken extensively about
OL,18,Fwanting to improve technical education
OL,19,Fand allow young people to make the
OL,20,Fchoice that works well for them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
