OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FMigration has been a thorny issue
OL,7,Fthrust to the forefront of voter
OL,8,Fconcerns in recent years.
OL,10,FUK net migration hit its lowest point
OL,11,Fsince 2012 (excluding the pandemic)
OL,12,Funder Starmer's leadership, dropping
OL,13,Fto 171,000 in the year to December
OL,14,F2025. Home Office figures show a 12%
OL,15,Fdecrease in those claiming asylum,
OL,16,Ffrom April 2025 to March 2026.
OL,18,FDuring his by-election campaign,
OL,19,FBurnham said that net migration needs
OL,20,Fto "fall further" than it has.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
