OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FOn Monday, Burnham voted in favour of
OL,7,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood's
OL,8,Fasylum reforms that aim to cut the
OL,9,Fnumber of small boat crossings and
OL,10,Finstead direct people to alternative
OL,11,F"safe and legal routes".
OL,13,FThese reforms are controversial among
OL,14,Fthe left of the Labour Party,
OL,15,Fespecially the changes to indefinite
OL,16,Fleave to remain (ILR).
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FMahmood plans to increase the time it
OL,7,Ftakes for people to be eligible for
OL,8,FILR from five years to ten, alongside
OL,9,Fother ideas like asylum seekers paying
OL,10,Fup to #10,000 towards the cost of
OL,11,Ftheir government support.
OL,13,FBalancing migration issues may be a
OL,14,Fdifficult balance for Burnham, who is
OL,15,Fseen as a soft-left politician.
OL,17,FWith the Ukraine war raging on and
OL,18,Fcontinued unrest in the Middle East,
OL,19,Fdefence is an area Burnham will need
OL,20,Fto be across very quickly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
