OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FDespite steadfast support for Ukraine,
OL,7,FStarmer's record on defence is a major
OL,8,Fflashpoint towards the end of his
OL,9,Fpremiership when defence secretary
OL,10,FJohn Healey resigned shortly before
OL,11,FStarmer announced the defence
OL,12,Finvestment plan (Dip), accusing the
OL,13,Foutgoing prime minister of making the
OL,14,Fcountry "less safe".
OL,16,FNew defence secretary Dan Jarvis
OL,17,Freceived #1.5 billion in additional
OL,18,Ffunding, totalling #15 billion, but
OL,19,Fthe plan leaves a #4.7 billion black
OL,20,Fhole, where it is unclear how the
OL,21,Fmoney will be raised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FBurnham has pledged to focus
OL,7,Finvestment on British defence firms
OL,8,Fand reduce foreign dependency, as part
OL,9,Fof the commitment in the Dip to
OL,10,Fincrease defence spending to 3.5% of
OL,11,Fgross domestic product (GDP) by 2035.
OL,13,FHe has said that Britain's support for
OL,14,FUkraine "will not waver," and he has
OL,15,Fbacked further sanctions against
OL,16,FIsraeli figures involved in settler
OL,17,Fviolence.
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
