OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FWhen Labour was elected in 2024, the
OL,7,Fparty promised not to raise income
OL,8,Ftax, VAT or national insurance
OL,9,Fcontributions for individuals. Burnham
OL,10,Fhas said he plans to stick to that.
OL,12,FIt is likely a budget will be set out
OL,13,Fby Burnham's chancellor in October,
OL,14,Fproviding a plan for how he will fund
OL,15,Fhis policies and ideas for change and
OL,16,Fhe has hinted there is "some room" for
OL,17,Fmovement on taxes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FBurnham has refused to rule out a
OL,7,Fwealth tax and said "we need a greater
OL,8,Fsense of fairness," but also said he
OL,9,Fwon't "demonise one group or create a
OL,10,Fnew way of dividing people".
OL,12,FHe has also pledged to overhaul
OL,13,Fbusiness rates, including higher taxes
OL,14,Fon out-of-town warehouses for online
OL,15,Fgiants such as Amazon, to help pay for
OL,16,Fcuts to rates for hospitality
OL,17,Fbusinesses.
OL,19,FBuilding relationships with foreign
OL,20,Fleaders, including Trump
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FThe outgoing PM was very comfortable
OL,7,Fon the world stage.
OL,9,FIn his final week, French President
OL,10,FEmmanuel Macron awarded him with the
OL,11,FLegion d'honneur, the first UK prime
OL,12,Fminister to receive the honour, given
OL,13,Ffor his work with France on the
OL,14,Fsecurity of Europe.
OL,16,FUkrainian leader Volodymyr Zelenskyy
OL,17,Ffollowed suit and presented Starmer
OL,18,Fwith the Order of Freedom, which is
OL,19,Fthe highest award for a foreign person
OL,20,Fin Ukraine during Starmer's final
OL,21,Fvisit to the country on Thursday.
OL,26,@sD@Brr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FBurnham has yet to be tested abroad,
OL,7,Fand his policy focus has so far
OL,8,Ffocused on the domestic issues in the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FAlthough Burnham has said he will
OL,12,Fspend less time on the international
OL,13,Fstage than his predecessor, Starmer
OL,14,Fwarned in an interview with the BBC
OL,15,Fthat foreign and domestic affairs are
OL,16,F"one and the same thing" and said he
OL,17,Fdid not think it was possible to spend
OL,18,Fless time on diplomacy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784575122
OL,3,CWelfare, tax and migration: The
OL,4,Cchallenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,6,FPresident Trump has already weighed in
OL,7,Fon Burnham, calling him "extremely
OL,8,Fliberal" and thought he "probably
OL,9,Fwon't open up the North Sea" for oil
OL,10,Fexploration, signalling a potential
OL,11,Frocky relationship between the pair
OL,12,Fbefore it's even begun.
OL,14,FThe new PM has previously criticised
OL,15,FTrump and, during his by-election
OL,16,Fcampaign, said US politics were
OL,17,F"poisonous".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
